debates.showAs: Insurance (Life Assurance and Life Insurance) (Amendment) Bill 2019: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to prohibit insurers, insurance providers, brokers or other such undertakings from failing or refusing to make payments under life insurance or assurance policies, including death benefit, where the person insured dies by suicide.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do thoirmeasc ar árachóirí, soláthraithe árachais, bróicéirí nó gnóthais eile den sórt sin mainneachtain íocaíochtaí faoi pholasaithe árachais saoil, lena n-áirítear sochar báis, a dhéanamh nó diúltú iad a dhéanamh, i gcás go bhfaighidh an duine árachaithe bás trí fhéinmharú.
bill.shortTitleEn: Insurance (Life Assurance and Life Insurance) (Amendment) Bill 2019

Equality (Miscellaneous Provisions) (No. 2) Bill 2017: Second Stage [Private Members]

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Employment Equality Act 1998 and the Equal Status Act 2000 by prohibiting discrimination on the basis of a person's mental health status and to provide for related matters
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú an Achta um Chomhionannas Fostaíochta, 1998 agus an Achta um Stádas Comhionann, 2000 trí thoirmeasc a chur ar idirdhealú ar bhonn stádas meabhairshláinte duine agus chun socrú a dhéanamh i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara

debates.showAs: Mental Health Parity Bill 2017: Second Stage [Private Members]
Mental Health Parity Bill 2017: Referral to Select Committee [Private Members]
Mental Health Parity Bill 2017: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to place mental health on parity with physical health; to improve the provision of mental health services; to increase the quality of care for those in mental health services; and to provide for related matters
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do chur na meabhairshláinte ar cothroime leis an tsláinte coirp; d'fheabhsú soláthar seirbhísí meabhairshláinte; d'ardú cháilíocht an  chúraim do dhaoine atá i seirbhísí meabhairshláinte; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara

act.longTitleEn: Act to amend and extend the Mental Health Act 2001; to make further and better provision relating to the treatment of persons under the Mental Health Act 2001; to improve the provision of mental health services; to promote the rights of persons subject to the Mental Health Act 2001; and to provide for related matters.
act.longTitleGa: Acht do leasú agus do leathnú an Achta Meabhair-Shláinte, 2001; do chorprú forálacha áirithe den Acht um Chinnteoireacht Chuidithe (Cumas), 2015 a bhaineann le cóireáil a chur ar othair faoin Acht Meabhair-Shláinte, 2001; d'fheabhsú soláthar seirbhísí meabhairshláinte; do dhéanamh cearta daoine atá faoi réir an Achta Meabhair-Shláinte, 2001 a chur chun cinn; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara
